
<div class="header">
<h1><strong>Creatures of the Bog!</strong></h1>
<p>Researchers at the local biology lab are exploring and documenting a series of bogs,
and the creatures of interest.
Here you can submit your findings
using our web application.</p>
</div>

<table class="whiten table table-condensed">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>


      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @creatures.each do |creature| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= creature.name %></td>
        <td><%= creature.description %></td>
      </tr>
        <td class="btn btn-primary btn-xs glyphicon glyphicon-ok-sign pull-left"><%= link_to 'Show', creature %></td>
        <td class="btn btn-primary btn-xs glyphicon glyphicon-pencil pull-left"><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_creature_path(creature) %></td>
        <td class="btn btn-danger btn-xs glyphicon glyphicon-trash pull-left"><%= link_to 'Destroy', creature, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<br>

<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
<button class="btn btn-primary btn-xs glyphicon glyphicon-plus pull-left"><%= link_to 'New Creature', new_creature_path %></button>
